snippet.title: Making of - X-Men Origins: Wolverine (video game)
snippet.description: Interview with the developers of the game based on the movie X-Men Origins: Wolverine, released in 2009 for PlayStation 3, Xbox 360, PlayStation 2, PSP, Wii and Nintendo DS.
